        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.3: \"The effect of 3 μm nicotine on DA release was reduced by half in both α4-/- and α6-/- animals (compared with α4+/+ and α6+/+ animals, respectively) and completely abolished in α4-/-α6-/- or β2-/- animals (Fig. 3A).\". Experimental description: \".... reduced the effect of 3 μm nicotine on DA release by 50% in α4+/+ or α6+/+ mice whole striatum ...\"" ;
